org.jamsim.ascape.weights

Class CategoricalVarAdjustment

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • org.jamsim.ascape.weights.CategoricalVarAdjustment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, TableModelListener, WeightCalculator, ParameterSet

    public class CategoricalVarAdjustment
extends Observable
implements WeightCalculator, TableModelListener
    Displays levels of a categorical variable across potentially multiple iterations and allows user to specify a proportion for each cell.
    Version:
    $Revision$
    Author:
